{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-flexbox/use-the-flex-direction-property-to-make-a-row","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"css-flexbox","demoType":null,"title":"Koristi svojstvo `flex-direction` za kreiranje reda","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Dodavanje <code>display: flex</code> na element ga pretvara u fleksibilni kontejner. Ovo omogućava porještanje bilo koje dete tog elementa u red ili kolonu. To radite dodavanjem svojstva <code>flex-direction</code> na roditeljski element i postavljanjem kao red ili kolonu. Kreiranje reda porješće dete horizontalno, a kreiranje kolone porješće dete vertikalno.</p>\n<p>Chaguzi nyingine za <code>flex-direction</code> ni <code>row-reverse</code> na <code>column-reverse</code>.</p>\n<p><strong>Napomena:</strong> Podrazumevana vrednost atributa <code>flex-direction</code> je <code>row</code>.</p>\n</section>","id":"587d78ab367417b2b2512af2","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Postavi atribut za CSS <code>flex-direction</code> na elementu <code>#box-container</code>, i dodeli mu vrednost od <code>row-reverse</code>.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":"https://scrimba.com/p/pVaDAv/cBEkbfJ","superBlock":"responsive-web-design","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301110,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-flexbox/use-the-flex-direction-property-to-make-a-row"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<style>\r\n  #box-container {\r\n    display: flex;\r\n    height: 500px;\r\n\r\n  }\r\n  #box-1 {\r\n    background-color: dodgerblue;\r\n    width: 50%;\r\n    height: 50%;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  #box-2 {\r\n    background-color: orangered;\r\n    width: 50%;\r\n    height: 50%;\r\n  }\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<div id=\"box-container\">\r\n  <div id=\"box-1\"></div>\r\n  <div id=\"box-2\"></div>\r\n</div>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Element <code>#box-container</code> mora imati svojstvo <code>flex-direction</code> postavljeno na <code>row-reverse</code>.</p>","testString":"const boxContainer = document.querySelector('#box-container');\r\nconst flexDirection = window.getComputedStyle(boxContainer)['flex-direction'];\r\nassert.strictEqual(flexDirection, 'row-reverse');"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/#css-flexbox","dashedName":"use-the-flex-direction-property-to-make-a-row","certification":"responsive-web-design","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"responsive-web-design","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"css-flexbox","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-flexbox/apply-the-flex-direction-property-to-create-rows-in-the-tweet-embed","prevChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-flexbox/add-flex-superpowers-to-the-tweet-embed","id":"587d78ab367417b2b2512af2","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":0,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"index","ext":"html","contents":"<style>\r\n  #box-container {\r\n    display: flex;\r\n    height: 500px;\r\n  }\r\n  #box-1 {\r\n    background-color: dodgerblue;\r\n    align-self: center;\r\n    height: 200px;\r\n    width: 200px;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  #box-2 {\r\n    background-color: orangered;\r\n    align-self: flex-end;\r\n    height: 200px;\r\n    width: 200px;\r\n  }\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<div id=\"box-container\">\r\n  <div id=\"box-1\"></div>\r\n  <div id=\"box-2\"></div>\r\n</div>","history":["index.html"],"fileKey":"indexhtml"}]}},"id":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-flexbox/use-the-flex-direction-property-to-make-a-row"}